items.title: RFK Jr. appoints longtime anti-vaccine ally Lyn Redwood to HHS position
items.description: Health Secretary Robert F. Kennedy Jr. has hired an anti-vaccine advocate and longtime ally to a position at the Health and Human Services Department.
